passive.name: New Chapter
passive.description: Increases the wearer's DEF by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color>. Increases the DMG of the wearer when they use their Ultimate by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of the wearer's DEF. This effect only applies 1 time per enemy target during each use of the wearer's Ultimate.
